title: Annual performance of the Dow Jones Composite Index 2000 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Index value in points. In total the number of data points it has is 20.
In general Index value in points has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2018 and 2019.
Maximum Index value in points, about 9386.48 was reported at Year 2019
Minimum Index value in points about 2374.96 was reached at Year 2002
